19:44.184 --> 19:45.269
Lyman!

19:45.352 --> 19:47.521
Great guy. Wired him all my money.

19:47.604 --> 19:48.689
He got us a house.

19:48.772 --> 19:50.816
Joseph Lyman sold us a house?

19:50.899 --> 19:52.234
Well, it's more of a shack.

19:52.317 --> 19:54.653
