drop everything and come with you?

19:57.823 --> 19:58.866
Well, yeah.

19:58.949 --> 20:00.701
It's the 19th century. You're my wife.

20:00.784 --> 20:02.035
I make the decisions.

20:02.119 --> 20:05.122
