I am not moving to Louisiana.

20:11.503 --> 20:13.130
I'd never see my family again.

20:13.630 --> 20:15.632
Not to mention,
I'd be on the wrong side of history.

20:15.716 --> 20:17.050
Hey, the South's not all bad.

20:17.134 --> 20:19.469
The plantation system,
it's more like an aristocracy--

20:19.553 --> 20:21.346
Slavery is bad, Ship.

20:21.430 --> 20:23.515
I thought you were all about
keeping an open mind.

20:23.599 --> 20:24.683
Not in this case.

20:24.766 --> 20:26.560
Come on. It'll be charming.

20:26.643 --> 20:28.020
