20:28.103 --> 20:29.938
I am a shrewd Yankee witch.

20:30.314 --> 20:31.940
-Respect that.
-I don't get it.

20:32.024 --> 20:33.317
You want me to leave you here

20:33.400 --> 20:35.569
and move down to Nola
and marry some cotton king's daughter?

20:35.652 --> 20:38.197
No, you-- you can marry me,

20:38.280 --> 20:42.117
we just have to stay in Amherst
and keep things loose and nonexclusive.

20:42.201 --> 20:43.202
Oh, my--

20:43.785 --> 20:44.912
Forget it.

20:45.454 --> 20:46.455
Forget it, man!

20:46.538 --> 20:49.541
I'm already in way over my head
on this shack.

20:51.210 --> 20:53.253
What-- Ship--

20:55.464 --> 20:56.924
Am I making a mistake?

20:57.007 --> 20:58.008
Yes.

20:58.091 --> 20:59.343
Absolutely.

20:59.426 --> 21:01.178
He wanted to marry you, Lavinia.

21:01.261 --> 21:03.722
Now you're gonna end up
a full-blown spinster.

21:09.061 --> 21:10.395
Same sheep, different day.

21:15.400 --> 21:16.693
Ship.

21:16.777 --> 21:18.153
Okay.

21:18.237 --> 21:20.239
-You go to New Orleans.
-Nola.

21:22.908 --> 21:24.117
Marry someone else.

21:24.826 --> 21:26.495
Have kids, all that shit.

21:27.496 --> 21:29.831
But you know, and I know...

21:30.499 --> 21:31.500
Yeah?

21:31.583 --> 21:35.212
...that I will always be the most
interesting girl you've ever loved.

