I dreamed this last night.

21:50.143 --> 21:51.144
What?

21:51.770 --> 21:53.981
-What are you talking about?
-I saw this happen.

21:56.275 --> 21:58.360
The church burning down. I had a vision.

21:59.069 --> 22:00.070
It came to me.

22:00.737 --> 22:02.573
I've seen all this before.

22:03.323 --> 22:05.158
No, you're imagining things.

22:05.242 --> 22:07.828
No. I dreamed about it last night,
and now it's real.

22:07.911 --> 22:09.830
Must be some terrible sign, a bad omen.

22:13.333 --> 22:15.836
All this talk of signs and visions.

22:16.336 --> 22:18.005
You sound as crazy as Emily.

22:20.257 --> 22:22.467
Or maybe she's not as crazy as we thought.

22:58.378 --> 22:59.588
Oh, my God.

