Not me.

25:19.228 --> 25:21.063
I feel sorry for the dead today.

25:23.440 --> 25:24.441
Emily?

25:25.817 --> 25:26.818
Yeah?

25:28.820 --> 25:30.030
When I'm with you...

25:31.990 --> 25:34.284
