To make you feel that way.

25:53.428 --> 25:55.848
I write for you, my Sue.

25:56.807 --> 25:58.016
I write for you.

26:00.602 --> 26:01.812
For you alone.

26:04.356 --> 26:05.649
That's enough.

26:10.445 --> 26:12.447
I will never let go of you again.
